Getting Started With Electrify Your Drumming

attributes.value: In this Student Focus, we review christiansantosa86, MattyPS, arunkr, I love Drumeo!, and sainsworths video submissions.

Michael Schack is a master at blending drum-set performance with cutting edge dance music. This pack will teach you all you need to know to approach many of the popular EDM styles of music that are so popular today - adding these types to your drumming will really modernize your approach to the drums!
This section will introduce you to EDM music and prepare you for all of the upcoming sections in Electrify Your Drumming.
